    {
      "bookmarkId": "609288_3_10617-10646",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "10617-10646",
      "markText": "我们美国人，便总是在强求其他民族采纳我们喜欢和习惯的信条。",
      "totalCount": 4230,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=609288&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=10617&rangeEnd=10646",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4132040594c08c41c28129?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=10617&rangeEnd=10646"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "609288_5_4513-4600",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "4513-4600",
      "markText": "鞠躬的意义标志着：本来可以自己处理的事，现在则承认了对方有权干预；而接受别人鞠躬的人还要承担起一定的责任。家庭生活正是以性别、辈分和长嗣继承等等为基础的等级制中最重要的核心。",
      "totalCount": 3584,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=609288&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4513&rangeEnd=4600",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4132040594c08c41c28129?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4513&rangeEnd=4600"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "609288_4_1584-1614",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1584-1614",
      "markText": "如此发达的日本应该让自己仍然落后的兄弟之邦——中国得到帮助。",
      "totalCount": 2669,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=609288&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1584&rangeEnd=1614",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4132040594c08c41c28129?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1584&rangeEnd=1614"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "609288_4_16577-16619",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "16577-16619",
      "markText": "只要选定一条路便奋不顾身全力以赴，倘若在这条路上失败，很自然地就重新选择其他的道路。",
      "totalCount": 2576,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=609288&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=16577&rangeEnd=16619",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4132040594c08c41c28129?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=16577&rangeEnd=16619"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "609288_3_7627-7657",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "7627-7657",
      "markText": "在微小的各个孤立行为的背后，彼此之间存在着一种系统性的联系。",
      "totalCount": 2486,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=609288&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=7627&rangeEnd=7657",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4132040594c08c41c28129?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=7627&rangeEnd=7657"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "609288_4_6111-6158",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "6111-6158",
      "markText": "不管是什么事，只有我们主动期求的，绝对没有我们被动接受的，更没有什么人能够强加给我们什么东西。",
      "totalCount": 2464,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=609288&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6111&rangeEnd=6158",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4132040594c08c41c28129?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6111&rangeEnd=6158"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "609288_10_5990-6054",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "5990-6054",
      "markText": "日本人将自己与自己从事的工作完全捆绑在一起，因此，如果你批评了某人的行为或工作能力，也就意味着你是在批评他的“名誉”和“自尊”。",
      "totalCount": 2159,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=609288&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=5990&rangeEnd=6054",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4132040594c08c41c28129?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=5990&rangeEnd=6054"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "609288_4_6547-6589",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "6547-6589",
      "markText": "总之，即使是溃不成军的惨败，也是在日本人的预料之中，并按照日本人已经想好的方向发展。",
      "totalCount": 2136,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=609288&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6547&rangeEnd=6589",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4132040594c08c41c28129?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6547&rangeEnd=6589"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "609288_3_4488-4559",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "4488-4559",
      "markText": "和其他东方民族相比，日本人似乎有着强烈的描述自我的爱好，他们在这样的描述中十分坦率，既有自己的生活琐事，也有国家全球扩张计划，这让人十分诧异。",
      "totalCount": 1995,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=609288&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4488&rangeEnd=4559",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4132040594c08c41c28129?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4488&rangeEnd=4559"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "609288_3_4781-4834",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "4781-4834",
      "markText": "为什么他们对于一些骇人听闻的残酷暴行不太在意反而对于一些看上去无足轻重的行为疯狂反击，这背后隐藏着什么呢？",
      "totalCount": 1952,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=609288&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4781&rangeEnd=4834",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4132040594c08c41c28129?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4781&rangeEnd=4834"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "609288_5_13395-13447",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "13395-13447",
      "markText": "对于封建制度进行破坏的往往就是商人阶级。如果一个社会的商人受到推崇，那么这个社会的封建制度就会很快衰亡。",
      "totalCount": 1898,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=609288&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=13395&rangeEnd=13447",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4132040594c08c41c28129?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=13395&rangeEnd=13447"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "609288_11_3223-3276",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "3223-3276",
      "markText": "日本人没有这些目的，他们睡觉就是为了睡觉，喜欢睡觉，因此只要没有人妨碍，他们就能踏踏实实地进入自己的梦乡。",
      "totalCount": 1870,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=609288&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=3223&rangeEnd=3276",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4132040594c08c41c28129?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=3223&rangeEnd=3276"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "609288_3_9014-9100",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "9014-9100",
      "markText": "我们忽略了一个民族的行为是基于这个民族的历史经验和不断传承、修订的价值体系才形成的，而我们却奢望与这样一套与我们的习惯有着很大不同的行为方式讲求共同的目标或者普世价值认同。",
      "totalCount": 1836,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=609288&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=9014&rangeEnd=9100",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4132040594c08c41c28129?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=9014&rangeEnd=9100"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "609288_4_2234-2267",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2234-2267",
      "markText": "日本总是向世界叫嚣他们必胜，而且非常坚信精神力量能够战胜物质力量。",
      "totalCount": 1806,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=609288&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2234&rangeEnd=2267",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4132040594c08c41c28129?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2234&rangeEnd=2267"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "609288_4_7925-7989",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "7925-7989",
      "markText": "事实上，现代日本的国家核心就是天皇，倘若美国挑战天皇的神圣性并且摧毁了天皇的存在，那么，现在日本的国家结构可能也会随之彻底坍塌。",
      "totalCount": 1728,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=609288&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=7925&rangeEnd=7989",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4132040594c08c41c28129?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=7925&rangeEnd=7989"
    },
    {
